KitKat::
She looked at Blackfang. She looked from toes to head. He had an 
impressive male form. She looke down at the little red bot next to 
her. She noticed that these were the two bots in the forest she had 
seen. She lowered her head and looked thoughtful for a moment. How as 
she watched them, for a moment, she wanted to join them. Perhaps even 
play with them. Her face plates showed longing and dispair.
